        <p id="about_us_head">ABOUT US</p>
            <p id="para">Welcome to Vanilla, your go-to destination for chic and contemporary bags. Founded by Khushi Pal, our brand is dedicated to providing high-quality, stylish, and functional bags for every occasion. Our collections are thoughtfully curated to offer a range of designs that cater to diverse tastes and lifestyles.</p>
        <p id="about_us_con">Our Mission</p>
            <p id="para">At Vanilla, our mission is to empower individuals with fashionable accessories that enhance their style and confidence. We believe in the power of a great bag to transform an outfit and make a statement. That's why we focus on creating versatile, durable, and beautiful bags that meet the needs of modern-day fashion enthusiasts.</p>
        <p id="about_us_con">Our Products</p>
            <p id="para">Our product range includes:</p>
